		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">mattmatteh wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">and it is only shorter if its an odd frame and backgound or sprites are enabled?</div><br /><br />yes<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">does skip a cycle if the background and sprites are off ?</div>
<br />
<br />no.  In that event the scanline takes the full 341.
<br />
<br />Blargg made some test ROMs which test this behavior in an emu -- they're on the wiki somewhere.  There's some documentation included which explains it in further detail.  I'd recommend checking that out.

		

